---
title: Mushroom and Spinach Stroganoff with Cardamon Rice
description: The original stroganoff was named after Count Pavel Stroganoff, a noted 19th century Russian diplomat and military commander. He lived in Paris but longed for the food of his homeland, so instructed his private chef (lucky him!) to create a French-Russian fusion dish ... and the stroganoff was born!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mushroom-and-spinach-stroganoff-9e85fb6a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/mushroom-and-spinach-stroganoff-1faba1ea.pdf
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
